<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bully" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bully,</orth> a brisk, dashing fellow: <cit><quote>discard, b. Hercules, cashier,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.3.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 3, 6</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>said I well, b. Hector?</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.3.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 3, 6</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>my hand, b.; thou shalt have egress and regress,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.225" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 225</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>bless thee, b. doctor,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.3.18" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 18</bibl></cit>. 29 etc. <cit><quote>b. knight,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.17" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 17</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>what sayest thou, b. Bottom?</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 8</bibl></cit>.* <cit><quote>O sweet b. Bottom!</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.2.19" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 19</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I love the lovely b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 48</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>